\Effect<SoftShake>Hayst! Why'd you kick the fricking anthill?!
Tumabi ka! This small guy is in my way.
Shut up Carl! You're gonna make things worse!
\Effect<HardVibe> \C[3] What a brave and foolish kid. You kicked my mound, without a care in the world.
\Effect<HardVibe> \C[3] You don't know what you have done.
\Effect<HardVibe> \C[3] Starting now those feet of yours that struck my resting place
will learn what it means to become useless.
That was a Nuno...I can't believe it cursed you...
First your moms casket had a sisiw
Then you go around kicking ant nuno's ant mounds...
and to top it off, you tried to go straight home after the wake without doing "pagpag".
It's a tradition...It means we don't go home yet. We stop. We buy something useless.
We wander around. We have to shake the spirit off our trail. If you go straight to your bedroom now, you're inviting the dead in with you.
You really are a magnet for curses, you know that?
Someone has to balance out my bad luck.
Dont make a big deal out of it.
Yeah, well. Someone has to say it.
Someone has to balance out my bad luck.
Oh, so thats my job now?
I'm not cursed. That was probably just some drunk guy with dwarfism.
Dont make a big deal out of it.
Ill make it a big deal if it keeps you alive.
Just dont do anything stupid again.
What the hell...my legs just gave up on me.
\Effect<HardShake> NUNO! PLEASE! IS THERE ANYTHING WE CAN DO TO LET CARL GO?
\Effect<HardVibe> \C[3] I would let this go, in one condition.
\Effect<HardVibe> \C[3] Somewhere in this forest are my favorite food. If you find them and give them to me before the sun sets...
\Effect<HardVibe> \C[3] I might just let this one go.
\Effect<SoftShake>Stay right there Carl! I'll find the ingredients!
\Effect<HardVibe> \C[3] Well you didn't find it in time.

\Effect<HardVibe> \C[3] Now get out of my forest and DON'T come back
Go, please! Don't worry about me.
\Effect<HardVibe> \C[3] Ahh, Tuba! The finest drink. That's another one.
\Effect<HardVibe> \C[3] Sticky rice! Oh how I love how it feels on my mouth.
